Bayraktarlar of Turkey Buys Out German Odelo Led, Dunya Says

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-06-27T05:49:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/bayraktarlar-of-turkey-buys-out-german-odelo-led-dunya-says.html
Bayraktarlar Holding AS, a Turkish
automotive parts maker, bought the whole of  Germany â€™s Odelo Led
GmbH, a manufacturer of car lighting equipment,  Dunya  reported,
citing deputy company chairman Ahmet Bayraktar.  Bursa, Turkey-based Bayraktarlar will merge Odelo with its
car parts maker unit Farba, he said, according to the newspaper.
Odelo had sales of 163 million euros in 2010 and Farba 40
million euros, he said.  Bayraktarlar aims to have a combined sales of 500 million
euros in 5 years and the group plans to build a car parts maker
in  China , Bayraktar said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
